{"tid":923500,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"領養代替購買","createTime":"2018-12-01T09:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T02:54:18.000Z","uid":16652,"like":72,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1dfe5e753fb7ac57f1f8edd63f3ad85faefec109","tid":923500,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"我覺得領養代替購買呢個觀念係幾好嘅<br />\n但點解要道德綁架我去領養呢<br />\n你揀男女朋友都會揀性格同個樣啦<br />\n何況係一隻陪你10年以上嘅寵物<br />\n條街咁多乞兒又唔見你去同佢地一齊佢哋咁慘<br />\n咁點解人哋成日話想買貓買狗就要講領養代替購買<br />\n如果第時想生仔成日有人話你不如去領養一個殘疾嘅孤兒啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇錯呀我為咗佢個樣佢嘅性格買佢又有乜問題呢<br />\n更何況，比起領養代替購買<br />\n我覺得更應該提倡無論發生乜事<br />\n都應該對自己養嘅寵物不離不棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b383ae3ac7f29a45fe056019c6b188021a3c6cd1","tid":923500,"uid":142313,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"不離不棄好難短時間內睇得出<br />\n但領養代替購買可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太難睇又想改變所以啲人先咁鍾意提倡領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0567518d57a40680e701a0aa9edc74e03d40c8af","tid":923500,"uid":142313,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b383ae3ac7f29a45fe056019c6b188021a3c6cd1","tid":923500,"uid":142313,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"不離不棄好難短時間內睇得出<br />\n但領養代替購買可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太難睇又想改變所以啲人先咁鍾意提倡領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:03:16.000Z","msg":"Btw雖然唔知真定假 但聽講有啲鋪頭為咗賣狗仔迫隻狗媽媽生到西到爛"},{"pid